thread.title_full: The Vet Shed reviewed by customer

author: customer
title: customer
text:
Excellent customer service and excellent products. A pleasure to deal with aND will do again.
My only downfall was the delivery time, but that isn't the vet sheds fault more the freight service. Said it was on van out for delivery 3 days ago and only just gother here. Not the first time I've had problems with the same company.
